node.text:
We had so much fun fixing our sister's new home up for her!  One of our favorite projects we built for her is this DIY Hairpin Console Table!  It's simple yet so chic at the same time!  The open base allows space for baskets to hide all the things, and it would be perfect in any room.  This is a super simple build, that requires minimal boards and tools! 

Get the free plans here --- https://www.shanty-2-chic.com/2020/02...

Metal Hairpin Legs --- https://rstyle.me/+fWqbHCvmqp8aOAhXml...

Metal Corner Pieces --- https://rstyle.me/+UOV9WW8jaNBBhfulBS...

Wood Stain --- https://rstyle.me/+8xUxJEI8S0z0n8x9CY...

Poly to finish --- https://rstyle.me/+uiz-03qeJUorPDo098...

Our Fav Wiping Rags for Staining --- https://rstyle.me/+JJ1S_8vsk8fawzFVsR...

Baskets for under the table --- https://rstyle.me/+aW2Hhky34olVwS24_g...

#shanty2chic #diy #howto #housecrash #reno #demo #building #console #table #entryway #budget

We have built so many dining tables over the last 10 years but one thing that we get so many requests for is a DIY Square Dining Table! We drove to Houston, TX to crash our sister's new house and one of her requests was a square dining table for her kitchen! This table seats 8 people and it's built with mostly framing lumber! So, let's build it! 

Get the free printable plans here - https://www.shanty-2-chic.com/2020/02...

We are back with another episode of our most recent #shantyhousecrash! Our baby sister just upgraded to a new house and we couldn't help but drive down to Houston to help her make it a home! No Shanty House Crash is complete without a DIY Dining Table, right?! I love this table so much. I love the price, the color, the angles, the size...I could go on! The best part about this table is that it was built with only 21 2x6 boards, making the total cost in lumber $129! Grab a cup of coffee and come build this dining table with us.

Free plans: @/diy-angle-base-dining-table.html

We teamed up with Furbo Dog Camera to keep an eye on our new pups while we are away at our shop building! We thought this DIY Dog Bed was the perfect project to test our new Furbo Dog Cameras out with! Now, we can keep an eye on them, feed them treats, talk to them and even get activity alerts, all while we are away from them and working in our shop! If you have a pup of your own, this is a must-have and it's so fun! Get your Furbo Dog Camera here -https://shopus.furbo.com/products/fur...

Get the free plans to build your own dog bed here - https://www.shanty-2-chic.com/2019/11...

GUYS!  Come check out the final reveal of our flip house!  We LOVE how it turned out and we hope you do too!  You can find links to all the goodies in this post, and we will be sharing a few more posts coming up with even more info!

https://www.shanty-2-chic.com/2019/10...​

Just a quick run down!

Link to Wood Plank Flooring - https://www.nfm.com/shaw-trilogy-that...​

We found the best carpet by Anderson Tuftex that we got through Nebraska Furniture Mart!
 - style: Scout ZZ073
 - color: 00511 Oyster Shell

Links to Appliances -
 - Refrigerator: https://www.nfm.com/lg-24-cu-ft-3-doo...​
 - Dishwasher: https://www.nfm.com/lg-top-control-wi...​
 - Range - https://www.nfm.com/lg-6-3-cu-ft-elec...​

We found the countertops at Nebraska Furniture Mart. They are made by Arizona Tile!

Paint Color Info - https://www.shanty-2-chic.com/2019/10...​

Our plumbing fixtures are all from Delta!  More info to come!

All lighting in the house are Capital Lighting fixtures that we got through Lighting Design Company!
You can see all their products here - https://lightingdesign.com/capital-li...​

Fireplace Tile is by Riad Tile! - https://www.riadtile.com​

All of our door knobs and handles are from Schlage!  We LOVE them! 

The rest of the tile in the house came from Floor&Decor!  We will be sharing more soon but check out their website here!  Great prices! - https://www.flooranddecor.com​

The barn wood we used for the vent hood and the master bedroom is the BOMB.  It is from our Reclaimed Designworks! https://www.reclaimeddesignworks.com​

Free Coffee Table Plans: https://www.shanty-2-chic.com/2019/09...​

node.text: I’ve been using my @kregjig 720 Pro for a few months now and I couldn’t love it more 🙌🏼🙌🏼 It’s made my building so much more efficient! The adjustable clamp is probably my favorite feature because it lets me switch between 3/4” and 1 1/2” lumber without adjusting the clamp 🤯🤯 Adding an Amazon link in our profile to purchase! #kregjig #shanty2chic #welovediy
